            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
            <span class="icon">📍</span>
            <h4>Prime Location</h4>
            <p>
                Located in the heart of the business district with excellent
                accessibility and nearby amenities.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


